import React from 'react'; import './Receipt.css' import img from './samples/receipt.png' import axios from 'axios' const Receipt=() => { let url = '/api/'+ number axios.get(url).then(function(res){ console.log(res.data); if(res.data!=null){ history.push('./car-details/'+number); } else { return(<> NO CAR EXISTS ) } }) return( <>
Parking Receipt

Parking Details

{p.id}
{p.color}, {p.model}
{p.plateNumber}
Slot No. :- {p.slot}
Parking History >
) } export default Receipt;
